:::Time Warp/The Protectrons/Torca/Ratchet/Sideswipe/Sky 
Lynx/Orion/Winterhart:::

::Time Warp hears Airbobmber shout. He runs to his postion::
Time Warp: There you are, brother.  So, you were absorbed by that monster bot 
too?
~~~~~
::My Maximals all breathe a sigh of releif when they watch the Alliance pull 
out::
Ratchet: Phew, that battle was TOO LONG!
Sideswipe: Agreed, my friend.
Sky Lynx: Eh, it wasnt SO bad.
Torca: C'mon Sky Lynx, your as damaged as the rest of us.
Orion: Yeah, get control of your ego.
Sky Lynx: Sorry, your right.
::Chromedome walks up to Iron Raptor::
Chromedome: You did well in this battle.  All the orders made by you were for 
the good of everyone. I havent seen a leader as good as you since my days 
with Fortress Maximus, and my group and i would be honored to serve you.  An 
alliance.  Do you accept my offer?
~~~~~
::The stasis pods DNA scanners reactivate, and they scan a white rabbit. The 
new Maximal climbs out. She looks around::
Winterhart: This must be earth. Winterhart, maximize!
::She transforms into very beautiful female robot mode and heads for the CF, 
with only instinct guiding her::

--part1_c0.ef915c5.27a24227_boundary
